description: Coveted corner 2 bed / 2 bath home at The Buckingham showcases sweeping views of Lakeshore East and Millennium Parks through dramatic floor-to-ceiling windows. A spacious entry foyer opens into a sun-drenched living and dining area with custom built-ins, perfect for both entertaining and everyday living.  The renovated kitchen features upgraded cabinetry, quartz counters, breakfast bar, and stainless-steel appliances.  The primary suite is massize and boasts a newly renovated spa-like bath with a glass-enclosed shower and soaking tub.  Second bedroom is 13 x 16, easily large enough for a guest bed and desk for those work from home days. A separate laundry room with washer/dryer and storage adds convenience.  The Buckingham is a premier, full-amenity building with a beautifully landscaped terrace, party room, heated indoor pool, sundeck, saunas, fitness center, bike room, guest parking, and attentive 24-hour door staff. Ideally located just steps from the lakefront, harbor, Grant, Millennium, and Maggie Daley Parks and Michigan Avenue.
